videos.description: Brionna Jones posts up the defender and makes the hook shot to extend Maryland's lead over Michigan State.
videos.headline: Maryland's Jones uses post move for bucket

videos.description: Shatori Walker-Kimbrough takes advantage of the poor defensive shift and makes the driving layup.
videos.headline: Maryland's Walker-Kimbrough left all alone for layup

videos.description: Stephanie Jones finishes the layup in transition after the great outlet pass.
videos.headline: Great passing leads to Maryland bucket in transition

videos.description: Brionna Jones finishes the layup after the great entry feed from Kristen Confroy.
videos.headline: Maryland pushes in transition for bucket

videos.description: Shatori Walker-Kimbrough comes up with the steal and then finishes on the other end with the layup.
videos.headline: Maryland turns defense into offense
